'''MainAd'''是一个国际广告技术公司，从事数字效果营销。公司总部位于意大利佩斯卡拉市。<ref name=":0">{{Cite web|url=https://www.crunchbase.com/organization/mainadv#/entity|title=MainAd {{!}} crunchbase|website=www.crunchbase.com|access-date=2017-03-08|archive-date=2019-06-05|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20190605092859/https://www.crunchbase.com/organization/mainadv#/entity|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref name="programmatic-italia.com">{{Cite news|url=http://www.programmatic-italia.com/marzan-chief-strategy-officer-mainad/|title=MainAd, Michele Marzan è il nuovo Chief Strategy Officer|date=2016-10-17|newspaper=Programmatic Italia|language=it|access-date=2016-11-16|archive-date=2020-12-03|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20201203033001/https://www.programmatic-italia.com/marzan-chief-strategy-officer-mainad/|dead-url=no}}</ref>

==背景==
公司于2007年成立。<ref>{{Cite web|url=http://www.pubblicitaitalia.it/2016101863524/digital/michele-marzan-entra-in-mainad-come-nuovo-chief-strategy-officer|title=Michele Marzan entra in MainAd come nuovo chief strategy officer {{!}} Pubblicità Italia|last=Meneghetti|first=website created by TVN S.r.l - www.televisionet.tv - Davide Catalano - Salvatore Lentini - Marco Arcangeli - Matteo|website=www.pubblicitaitalia.it|access-date=2016-11-16|archive-date=2019-06-13|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20190613164503/https://www.pubblicitaitalia.it/2016101863524/digital/michele-marzan-entra-in-mainad-come-nuovo-chief-strategy-officer|dead-url=no}}</ref>

MainAd在2016年4月时改变品牌，将原公司名mainADV中的v去掉，<ref>{{Cite news|url=http://www.engage.it/agenzie/mainad/77581|title=MainAd è Silver Sponsor dello Iab Seminar sul Performance|date=2016-07-06|newspaper=Engage {{!}} News and views sul marketing pubblicitario|language=it|access-date=2016-11-16|archive-date=2016-11-25|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20161125174558/http://www.engage.it/agenzie/mainad/77581|dead-url=no}}</ref>变成现在的MainAd。MainAd在[[米兰|米兰]]，[[伦敦|伦敦]]，[[巴黎|巴黎]]，[[伊斯坦布尔|伊斯坦布尔]]，[[迪拜|迪拜]]，[[圣地亚哥_(智利)|圣地亚哥 (智利)]]，[[马尼拉|马尼拉]]，[[锡鲁万纳塔普拉姆|锡鲁万纳塔普拉姆]]，[[班加罗尔|班加罗尔]]都设有分公司。<ref name="programmatic-italia.com"/><ref>{{Cite web|url=https://www.crunchbase.com/organization/mainadv/addresses|title=MainAd - Offices/Locations {{!}} crunchbase|website=www.crunchbase.com|access-date=2016-11-16|archive-date=2016-11-26|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20161126001341/https://www.crunchbase.com/organization/mainadv/addresses|dead-url=no}}</ref>

MainAd为广告商提供重定向、品牌展示、客户抓取等服务。在他们重定向服务中，他们可为广告商们免费提供动态广告横幅设计。通过分析用户网页浏览行为，广告主可以选择想展示的文字内容，以此来更好地对定向人群展示对他们感兴趣的广告内容。MainAd使用内部及第三方技术来提供服务。

MainAd是英国和意大利互动广告局的成员之一。<ref>{{Cite news|url=http://www.engage.it/eventi/performance-marketing-iab-seminar/74412|title=Iab presenta il Seminar sul Performance Marketing - Engage.it|date=2016-06-09|newspaper=Engage {{!}} News and views sul marketing pubblicitario|language=it|access-date=2016-11-22|archive-date=2019-06-19|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20190619200833/https://www.engage.it/eventi/performance-marketing-iab-seminar/74412|dead-url=no}}</ref>

MainAd从2011年开始支持意大利地球社。<ref>{{Cite web|url=http://terredeshommes.it/mainadfundraiser/|title=MainAd fundraiser|website=terredeshommes.it|access-date=2016-11-16|archive-date=2019-06-17|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20190617140310/https://terredeshommes.it/mainadfundraiser/|dead-url=no}}</ref>

